reviewText: Video was very useless, poor recording

Another great educational video by Aesthetic Video Source, this one on how to style and work with African American skin types when applying makeup. From this video, I got the most out of showing you how to bleach brows to contour the face. Like their other videos, wonderful closeup make it better than sitting in a class all day 10-20 feet away. With this video, you can see exactly how the instructor interacts with clients and the detail brush precision movements.
